If you use "deploy-tls-termination-controller-ELB.yaml" you don't need to specify secrets inside Ingress,

step: 1 create image and put to ecr
step: 2 using ecr image create deployment
step: 3 create services for each deployment as ClusterIP
step: 4 setup Ingress controller with ACM SSL(it is a single file which will deploy all below), if NLB specify ssl inside Service, if ELB then specify ssl inside Ingress as secrets
  - ConfigMap
  - IngressControleer
  - ServiceAccount
  - Load Balancer Service
    etc.
